{"tid":1563741,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"按揭問題 有冇銀行按揭巴打答答","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:30:00.000Z","uid":45370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20cf72a58c651bd965d2bdf5f250b54074da2bdc","tid":1563741,"uid":45370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"我有一份受薪工作 穩定收入 比到糧單有供mpf<br />\n<br />\n但同時間呢兩年揾會計開左間公司報稅 <br />\n間公司就蝕緊錢 <br />\n<br />\n想問下如果做按揭八成 係咪一定要稅單<br />\n<br />\n同埋係咪只係要上一個年度報左稅就得<br />\n例如六月買樓 四月底報左係咪就用得呢張稅單比銀行<br />\n<br />\n求解答 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d8d8654b1215d1d2511f0dda04701768d82fa9","tid":1563741,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ca21f1fa626b5a8996807e85a059881c8b13d95f","tid":1563741,"uid":45370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"915 謝謝巴打幫推"},{"pid":"5a04651d3d796afb67f995ce0ea35f773fe7e460","tid":1563741,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"咁既時勢 祝你好運"},{"pid":"466a34b54a5ec59a3234fb1d792cd9fb2e03e3c9","tid":1563741,"uid":45370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu